def iter():
    pipeline=[
    {"$match":{"area":"海淀"}},
    {"$group":{"_id":"$cates","counts":{"$sum":1}}},
    {"$sort":{"counts":-1}},
    {"$limit":3},
]
    for i in info.aggregate(pipeline):
        data={
             'type': 'column',
             'name': i["_id"],
             'data': [i["counts"],]
        }
        yield data

for i in info.find():
    try:
        print(i["price"])
        if isinstance(i["price"],str) and i["price"].find("元")!=-1:
            price=float(i["price"].replace("元",""))
        elif isinstance(i["price"],str) and i["price"].find("面议")!=-1:
            price=-1
        elif i["price"]=="none":
            price=-1
        elif i["price"]=="${info.paramsMap.minprice}":
            price=-1
        else:
            price=float(i["price"])
        info.update({"_id":i["_id"]},{"$set":{"price":price}})
    except ValueError  as e:
        price=-1
        info.update({"_id":i["_id"]},{"$set":{"price":price}})

def iter2():
